<paragraph blockId="8.[675,1212,1516,1699]" pageId="8" pageNumber="673">
DIAGNOSIS. — Medium size scorpions: male 
<quantity box="[1113,1184,1516,1540]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.2" pageId="8" pageNumber="673" unit="mm" value="52.0">52 mm</quantity>
in total length. Coloration yellowish to slightly reddishyellow, with some dark zones on pedipalp carinae.Pectines with 7-7 teeth in males. Hemispermatophore as in 
<figureCitation box="[679,784,1622,1646]" captionStart="FIG" captionStartId="9.[113,124,1658,1675]" captionTargetBox="[207,1078,225,1588]" captionTargetId="figure-17@9.[149,1175,189,1623]" captionTargetPageId="9" captionText="FIG. 6. — Opisthacanthus pauliani n. sp., ♂ holotype: A, carapace; B, chelicera; C, ventral aspect, showing coxapophysis, sternum, genital operculum, pectines and sternite III; D, hemispermatophore, external aspect. Scale bars: 2 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5753786" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5753786/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="673">Figure 6D</figureCitation>
. Male genital operculum large and slightly heart-like shaped (
<figureCitation box="[863,942,1649,1673]" captionStart="FIG" captionStartId="9.[113,124,1658,1675]" captionTargetBox="[207,1078,225,1588]" captionTargetId="figure-17@9.[149,1175,189,1623]" captionTargetPageId="9" captionText="FIG. 6. — Opisthacanthus pauliani n. sp., ♂ holotype: A, carapace; B, chelicera; C, ventral aspect, showing coxapophysis, sternum, genital operculum, pectines and sternite III; D, hemispermatophore, external aspect. Scale bars: 2 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5753786" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5753786/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="673">Fig. 6C</figureCitation>
). Trichobothrial pattern of 
<typeStatus box="[678,720,1675,1699]" pageId="8" pageNumber="673">type</typeStatus>
C, orthobothriotaxy.
</paragraph>
<caption ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5753786" ID-Zenodo-Dep="5753786" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5753786/files/figure.png" pageId="9" pageNumber="674" startId="9.[113,124,1658,1675]" targetBox="[207,1078,225,1588]" targetPageId="9">
